Expense Splitter:
1) Personal accounts for each person
2) Individual expense maintainer
3) Group expense maintainer
4) Note type of expense
5) Spilt groupwise,individual or even among particular set of people
6) History of expenses: Both pending and settled
7) Settle expenses: E-Wallet, UPI, NetBanking, Card or Cash
8) Set credit limit, shouldnt allow to spend above that. Give alerts
9) Monthly expenses - Electricity, water, loans, emis groceries, wifi, Phone etc.

DataBase Schema:

USER:

U_ID          : INT PRIMARY KEY AUTO_INCREMENT           
USER_NAME     : VARCHAR(25)
EMAIL_ID      : VARCHAR(50)
PASSWORD      : VARCHAR(25)
EXPENSE_LIMIT : FLOAT
CREATED_AT    : DATE TIMESTAMP 
UPDATED_AT    : DATE TIMESTAMP

EXPENSE:

E_ID          : INT PRIMARY KEY AUTO_INCREMENT
U_ID          : INT FOREIGN KEY REFERENCES USER(U_ID)
CATEGORY_ID   : INT FOREIGN KEY REFERENCES CATEGORY_TYPE(CATEGORY_ID)
TYPE_ID       : INT FOREIGN KEY REFERENCES EXPENSE_TYPE(TYPE_ID)
DESCRIPTION   : VARCHAR(100)
AMOUNT        : FLOAT
DATE          : DATE TIMESTAMP
CREATED_AT    : DATE TIMESTAMP 
UPDATED_AT    : DATE TIMESTAMP


GROUP:

G_ID          : INT PRIMARY KEY AUTO_INCREMENT
GROUP_NAME    : VARCHAR(25)
CREATED_AT    : DATE TIMESTAMP 
UPDATED_AT    : DATE TIMESTAMP


GROUP_MEMBERS:

G_ID          : INT FOREIGN KEY REFERENCES GROUP(G_ID)
U_ID          : INT FOREIGN KEY REFERENCES USER(U_ID)
CREATED_AT    : DATE TIMESTAMP 
UPDATED_AT    : DATE TIMESTAMP


GROUP_EXPENSE:

SPLIT_ID      : INT PRIMARY KEY AUTO_INCREMENT
E_ID          : INT FOREIGN KEY REFERENCES EXPENSES(E_ID)
G_ID          : INT FOREIGN KEY REFERENCES GROUP(G_ID)
CREATED_AT    : DATE TIMESTAMP 
UPDATED_AT    : DATE TIMESTAMP


EXPENSE_MEMBERS: 

SPLIT_ID      : FOREIGN KEY REFERENCES GROUP_EXPENSE(SPLIT_ID)
U_ID          : FOREIGN KEY REFERENCES USER(U_ID)
PENDING       : BOOLEAN
AMOUNT        : FLOAT
CREATED_AT    : DATE TIMESTAMP 
UPDATED_AT    : DATE TIMESTAMP


EXPENSE_TYPE:

TYPE_ID       : INT PRIMARY KEY AUTO_INCREMENT
TYPE          : VARCHAR(20)
CREATED_AT    : DATE TIMESTAMP 
UPDATED_AT    : DATE TIMESTAMP


CATEGORY_TYPE

CATEGORY_ID      : INT PRIMARY KEY AUTO_INCREMENT
CATEGORY_TYPE    : VARCHAR(25)
CREATED_AT       : DATE TIMESTAMP 
UPDATED_AT       : DATE TIMESTAMP




